  • Mobile Devices

    If you are accessing the Blackboard from your mobile devices, use the MOODLE APP. You can download this from your app store.

    ***TO ACCESS CLASSES FROM MOBILE***



    MOBILE DEVICES: TO GO TO OUR COACH BLACKBOARD ON MOBILE, DOWNLOAD MOODLE

    When you open the app it will ask for a URL or QR Code. Use https://coachhomeschool.org 


    TO SWITCH TO YOUR KIDS ACCOUNTS:

    Under top right profile link drop down and click "Switch Accounts" You will need to log in one time for each of them, then you can easily switch accounts.
